  "texts": [
    "Additionally, current datasets prioritize Western sensory profiles, which underrepresent global diversity.",
    "Furthermore, few studies address the ethical implications of AI-driven sensory manipulation in consumer products.",
    "Motivated by these considerations, this review examines the current state of AI applications in olfactory and gustatory research, highlighting advanced methodologies, representative case studies, interdisciplinary implications, and existing limitations.",
    "Unlike previous reviews that address olfaction and gustation separately, this work integrates the two modalities into a unified analytical framework.",
    "This integration clarifies how AI techniques can model the interplay between odor and taste, an aspect often overlooked in single-modality analyses."
